Former Zanu PF Chitungwiza South legislator, Christopher Chigumba, has died. Chigumba succumbed to COVID-19. Chigumba is said to have died at a local hospital where he had been admitted. Mourners are gathered in Tynwald, Harare. Chigumba was father to Mac Christopher Chigumba (Jnr), ex-husband to Zimbabwe Electoral Commission (ZEC) Chairperson, Priscilla Makanyara Chigumba. More details to followâ€¦  